{"text_id":56730,"tokens":["In"," my"," opinion",","," students"," should"," indeed"," be"," required"," to"," maintain"," a"," certain"," grade"," point"," average"," (","GPA",")"," to"," participate"," in"," school"," sports","."," This"," requirement"," is"," not"," only"," fair"," but"," also"," essential"," for"," the"," academic"," well","-","being"," of"," students",".","\n\n","First"," and"," foremost",","," the"," primary"," purpose"," of"," schools"," is"," to"," educate"," students",","," not"," to"," groom"," athletes","."," Academic"," performance"," should"," always"," take"," precedence"," over"," extracurricular"," activities","."," By"," setting"," a"," minimum"," GPA"," requirement",","," schools"," can"," ensure"," that"," students"," prioritize"," their"," studies"," and"," do"," not"," compromise"," on"," their"," academic"," performance"," for"," the"," sake"," of"," sports","."," This"," approach"," will"," help"," maintain"," a"," healthy"," balance"," between"," academics"," and"," athletics",".","\n\n","Another"," crucial"," aspect"," is"," that"," sports"," participation"," is"," a"," privilege",","," not"," a"," right","."," By"," requiring"," students"," to"," meet"," a"," certain"," GPA"," threshold",","," schools"," can"," incul","cate"," a"," sense"," of"," responsibility"," and"," accountability"," among"," students","."," This"," approach"," will"," encourage"," students"," to"," take"," their"," studies"," seriously",","," which"," will"," ultimately"," lead"," to"," better"," academic"," outcomes","."," For"," instance",","," a"," study"," conducted"," by"," the"," National"," Federation"," of"," State"," High"," School"," Associations"," found"," that"," student","-","athletes"," who"," maintained"," a"," higher"," GPA"," were"," more"," likely"," to"," graduate"," from"," college"," and"," secure"," better"," job"," opportunities",".","\n\n","Moreover",","," maintaining"," a"," minimum"," GPA"," requirement"," can"," also"," have"," a"," positive"," impact"," on"," the"," overall"," athletic"," performance"," of"," the"," team","."," When"," student","-","athletes"," are"," focused"," on"," their"," studies",","," they"," are"," more"," likely"," to"," be"," motivated",","," disciplined",","," and"," goal","-","oriented",","," which"," are"," essential"," qualities"," for"," success"," in"," sports","."," A"," study"," by"," the"," National"," Center"," for"," Education"," Statistics"," found"," that"," student","-","athletes"," who"," performed"," well"," academically"," tended"," to"," perform"," better"," in"," their"," respective"," sports",".","\n\n","In"," conclusion",","," requiring"," students"," to"," maintain"," a"," certain"," GPA"," to"," participate"," in"," school"," sports"," is"," a"," prudent"," decision"," that"," benefits"," both"," the"," students"," and"," the"," school","."," It"," promotes"," academic"," excellence",","," incul","c","ates"," responsibility",","," and"," fosters"," a"," healthy"," balance"," between"," academics"," and"," athletics","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}